lol, Lookinforwalleye, I thought of you when the fans at the ACC boo'd Chara whenever he touched the puck.  Despite our oldschool rivalry, Leafs fans clearly have your back.  I don't know why or how the bruins failed to show up tonight but this game is very fun to watch from a leaf perspective.  As soon as Leaf playoff hopes are lost, the next best Canadian team becomes my focus.  Hopefully the first round matchup is Habs v Bruins that would be awesome.
